```

| Part  | Element           | Key Attributes                                                                                                  |
| ----- | ----------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Root  | `<span>`          | `data-ars-scope="highlight"`, `data-ars-part="root"`, `dir="auto"`                                              |
